title: Looking For Strong Mid Laners (Diamond 5 / Platinum 1+) Competitive Ranked 5's!
body:
Looking for most importantly Mids but if you are JG/Top also interested in **competitive ranked 5's team.** 

Times of playing I am looking to start** 4:30 - 8:30 AEST weekdays.** Then more flexible times weekend.

So if interested in playing competitive ranked 5's add me in game **"Commando"**
